title: Jim Cramer says to buy Facebook, Amazon and AMD instead of chasing airline and cruise stocks
text: "Mad Money" host Jim Cramer said the surging airline and cruise stocks need economic tailwinds to justify their valuations.

title: Nasdaq Composite Hits 10,000; FANG Stocks Showing Strength
text: The Nasdaq composite led on Tuesday while the S&P 500 took a little break.

title: Amazon, Apple, Facebook and Microsoft close at all-time highs as Big Tech rallies back from coronavirus
text: The combined market value of the four companies is now close to $5 trillion, with Apple claiming the top spot at nearly $1.5 trillion.

title: Facebook News launches to all in U.S. with addition of local news and video
text: Facebook News, the social network’s dedicated section devoted to journalism, is today launching for all users in the U.S. The feature was first introduced in October 2019 as a limited test in the U.S.

title: Facebook Rolls out Inbox on Messenger to Help Businesses Communicate with Customers
text: Facebook has been courting small businesses ever since the pandemic hit the U.S.

title: Facebook’s Advantage Over Other Social Media
text: Discover the elements that define Facebook, which boasts 2.6 billion monthly active users, who cement the company as the world's top social media outlet.

title: FAANG Rally Continues as Players Cash in on Coronavirus Crisis
text: While most industries have taken a beating due to the coronavirus outbreak, FAANG stocks have not only survived the pandemic but also put up a great show.
